<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/1910836-lobstergirl"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1380256801i/1910836._UX100_CR0,16,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
