<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/1910836-lobstergirl">Lobstergirl</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">From the wikipedia page: &quot;Cities of salt,&quot; said Munif when asked by Tariq Ali to explain the book&apos;s title, &quot;means cities that offer no sustainable exi<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">From the wikipedia page: "Cities of salt," said Munif when asked by Tariq Ali to explain the book's title, "means cities that offer no sustainable existence. When the waters come in, the first waves will dissolve the salt and reduce these great glass cities to dust. In antiquity, as you know, many cities simply disappeared. It is possible to foresee the downfall of cities that are inhuman. With no means of livelihood they won't survive."<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
