<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1017689-i-understand-this-is-the-first-volume-of-a">I understand this is the first volume of a trilogy, but I cannot find a translation of the other two. Can it be read as a standalone ? I find it hard to finish a book with loose ends, knowing something else comes after but unable to read it.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1017689'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F2722.Cities_of_Salt">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1017689-i-understand-this-is-the-first-volume-of-a">4 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1017689-i-understand-this-is-the-first-volume-of-a">Add your answer</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

