<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/59240359-ahmed-fouadeldin"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1539087582i/59240359._UY100_CR16,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/59240359-ahmed-fouadeldin">Ahmed Fouadeldin</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Yes you can, and probably should, also it is a quintet not a trilogy yet you can read the first volume as a standalone and I think you will love it.<br/>As<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Yes you can, and probably should, also it is a quintet not a trilogy yet you can read the first volume as a standalone and I think you will love it.<br />As for the translation the first three parts only were translated and you can find them easily online but the last two aren't.<br /><a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
