        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer95687343" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7044786668841936824">Sort of the Grapes of Wrath of the Arabian Peninsula. Munif&apos;s descriptions of the socio-economic changes brought by an American oil company on the Arab Bedouin communities are superb. Excellent translation. Brings the history of oil politics and the effects of early oil exploration in the Persian gulf alive. It&apos;s refreshing to read an Arab perspective. If you are interested in reading some Arab fiction this is highly recommended.</span>
  <span id="freeText7044786668841936824" style="display:none">Sort of the Grapes of Wrath of the Arabian Peninsula. Munif's descriptions of the socio-economic changes brought by an American oil company on the Arab Bedouin communities are superb. Excellent translation. Brings the history of oil politics and the effects of early oil exploration in the Persian gulf alive. It's refreshing to read an Arab perspective. If you are interested in reading some Arab fiction this is highly recommended.</span>
