    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_181681344" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/181681344" />
    <a title="Debbie" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/5672040-debbie"><img alt="Debbie" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1414517624p2/5672040.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/181681344?book_show_action=true">Jul 03, 2011</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Debbie" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Debbie" href="/user/show/5672040-debbie">Debbie</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5672040-debbie?shelf=100-most-influential">100-most-influential</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer181681344" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17510999054621373430">#71 on the Novel 100 list.<br/>What an intriguing book! Focused on the cultural clash that occurred in the Middle East when oil was discovered, it was a fascinating look into the devastating consequences of greed and the challenge of moving past the language barrier to really understanding another culture.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


