<div id="review_2719232912" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2719232912" />
    <a title="Jayanti Banerjee" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/17199096-jayanti-banerjee"><img alt="Jayanti Banerjee" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1360165378p2/17199096.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2719232912?book_show_action=true">Feb 24, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jayanti Banerjee" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jayanti Banerjee" href="/user/show/17199096-jayanti-banerjee">Jayanti Banerjee</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback " href="/book/show/5948927">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2719232912" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1546761187168287179">I read City of Salt in its English translation. What a powerful telling of a form of colonialism and the effect it has upon the society it enters.<br/>But a slow tale ... sometimes with digressions I didn’t fully understand. My education has only just begun.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

