<li class='cover' id='bookCover_5948932'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/5948932"><img alt="شرق المتوسط" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1227863497l/5948932._SX98_.jpg" />
